-Cancellation from `REQUEST_RESERVED` requires complete hash-bound capture and process-launch snapshots proving zero STARTED rows, zero launch evidence, and zero terminal capture rows for the full reservation interval; irreversible closure of the reservation; and an explicit old-authorization unusable flag. Any missing or contradictory evidence is `RESERVATION_START_STATUS_UNPROVEN` and is not continuation eligibility.
